org.deviceconnect.android.profile

クラス TouchProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.DConnectProfile
      • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.TouchProfile
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    DConnectProfileConstants, TouchProfileConstants

    public class TouchProfile
extends DConnectProfile
implements TouchProfileConstants
    Touch Profile.

    API that provides a smart device touch operation function.
    Device plug-in that provides a touch operation function by extending this class, and implements the corresponding API that.

    API provides methods

    The request to each API of Touch Profile, following callback method group is automatically invoked.
    Subclass is to implement the functionality by overriding the method for the API provided by the device plug-in from the following methods group.
    Features that are not overridden automatically return the response as non-compliant API.

    • Touch API [GET] : onGetOnTouch(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Touch Start API [GET] : onGetOnTouchStart(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Touch End API [GET] : onGetOnTouchEnd(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Double Tap API [GET] : onGetOnDoubleTap(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Touch Move API [GET] : onGetOnTouchMove(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Touch Cancel API [GET] : onGetOnTouchCancel(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Touch Event API [Register] : onPutOnTouch(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnTouch(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Start Event API [Register] : onPutOnTouchStart(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Start API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnTouchStart(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch End Event API [Register] : onPutOnTouchEnd(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch End API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnTouchEnd(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Double Tap Event API [Register] : onPutOnDoubleTap(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Double Tap API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnDoubleTap(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Move Event API [Register] : onPutOnTouchMove(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Move API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnTouchMove(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Cancel Event API [Register] : onPutOnTouchCancel(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Touch Cancel API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnTouchCancel(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    作成者:
    NTT DOCOMO, INC.
